{"tid":1564014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"915 唔批遊行，咁我地仲可以做咩","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:55:24.000Z","uid":42149,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b727ad4aab721cf2b10db4a4465b7e79552512","tid":1564014,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"而家警犬批唔批不反對通知書都唔係問題。<br />\n係批同唔批都係咁行。<br />\n各位！休息左一個星期，歌又唱過，會又集過。<br />\n係時候收拾心情，準備好915行街罷買大活動<br />\n<br />\n記住，我地仲未贏。我諗我地贏左10%都唔知有冇<br />\n太子有手足失蹤<br />\n有女手足比黑警非禮<br />\n有大量手捉被起訴<br />\n<br />\n我地要搵返初心，五大訴求<br />\n我地點解可以行左三個月都仲咁有火<br />\n因為我地五大訴求。決一不可<br />\n<br />\n我地呢場革命，係一定要贏，如果輸，就輸十年<br />\n<br />\n915, 遮打見<br />\n<br />\n光復香港。時代革命"},{"pid":"e5c7ca4d8811c8d7bdfb2b95399bd5c5fb440c2c","tid":1564014,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bd51982bae73d89e7b1c21bf5828ac1cd64e9f59","tid":1564014,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"157c7b55a8ea07faf012981b4f6a629b55a